      <Value><![CDATA[<p><strong>Reading for Study</strong></p>
<p>There is a great deal, potentially, to read at university, and generally not much guidance about what and how much you read. It is Important to develop active reading skills to help you be selective and critical about your reading.</p>]]></Value>
